{"tid":40141,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[恐佈食堂] 點解金太郎咁垃圾都未執？？","createTime":"2016-12-15T04:16:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-13T15:23:40.000Z","uid":1171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c5f3a2edb53f182587e1620f7241256919fa595a","tid":40141,"uid":1171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T04:16:46.000Z","msg":"話說呢間垃圾日本野<br />\n垃圾到爆都已經唔使講<br />\n壽司飯好似假野咁一夾就散(應該話係無痴埋過一舊)<br />\n綠茶粉包冲極都無綠茶味出黎齋飲滾水<br />\nD枱又細到擺多兩個碟都無位就黎要用個頭頂住d碟(order枱，不是指回轉枱)<br />\n上次隔離台跌左舊雞落地下，唔使30秒有差不多過百隻蟻衝出黎⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n點解可以維持咁多年都未執<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef40d2f33846d1185f3a8fefa307c3aee937a2fa","tid":40141,"uid":50327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T04:19:27.000Z","msg":"以前搵得少，拍拖想食日本野都靠佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家食爭鮮都唔食佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1acd340e8ef8248d941275c144afc22a3f26280c","tid":40141,"uid":11980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T04:20:44.000Z","msg":"無記錯既話仲要同元氣差唔多貴（2,3年前食）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"571006ee727336fdc71540535873e27e7e4a7b0f","tid":40141,"uid":13474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T04:37:03.000Z","msg":"下屌間野食日本野架？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43baa9fbe01de98ea8d27446227c6b8233ac69df","tid":40141,"uid":187489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c5f3a2edb53f182587e1620f7241256919fa595a","tid":40141,"uid":1171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T04:16:46.000Z","msg":"話說呢間垃圾日本野<br />\n垃圾到爆都已經唔使講<br />\n壽司飯好似假野咁一夾就散(應該話係無痴埋過一舊)<br />\n綠茶粉包冲極都無綠茶味出黎齋飲滾水<br />\nD枱又細到擺多兩個碟都無位就黎要用個頭頂住d碟(order枱，不是指回轉枱)<br />\n上次隔離台跌左舊雞落地下，唔使30秒有差不多過百隻蟻衝出黎⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n點解可以維持咁多年都未執<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"repl